<subSubSection id="A8EF386CEADA5A9C9F01A2152CE45809" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="5368F8FACBDE0509AC026426A6BC5BA1" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A701664905695D786F57C96AB60199AC" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">This species is dedicated to Dr. Beatriz Toro Restrepo, Universidad de Caldas, in recognition of her work in environmental education, friendship and contributions in fieldwork with aquatic insects of Colombia.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
